---
import Reason1 from "../Icons/Reason/Reason1.astro";
import Reason2 from "../Icons/Reason/Reason2.astro";
import Reason3 from "../Icons/Reason/Reason3.astro";
import Reason4 from "../Icons/Reason/Reason4.astro";
---

<section class="flex flex-col min-h-[70vh] items-center justify-center ">
    <h2 class=" text-3xl font-semibold relative mb-8 mt-8">
        ¿Por qué elegirnos? 
        <span class="block w-[100%] h-1 bg-[#7f3812] pt-2 mt-2"></span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 mb-8">
      <div class="group relative dark:bg-[#7f3812]/30 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center overflow-hidden transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
        <div class="h-96 w-72">
          <Reason1 class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-3 group-hover:scale-125"/>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b group-hover:from-black/70 group-hover:via-black/60 group-hover:to-black/70"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex translate-y-[60%] flex-col items-center justify-center px-9 text-center transition-all duration-500 group-hover:translate-y-0 ">
          <h1 class="font-dmserif text-3xl font-bold dark:text-[#e4aa0f] text-black  group-hover:text-white ">Ahorro</h1>
          <p class="mb-3 text-lg italic text-white opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100">Ofrecemos las mejores ofertas y descuentos para que puedas disfrutar de tus viajes sin comprometer tu presupuesto.</p>
          <button class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 py-2 px-3.5 font-com text-sm capitalize text-white shadow shadow-black/60">See More</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative dark:bg-[#7f3812]/30 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center overflow-hidden transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
        <div class="h-96 w-72">
          <Reason2 class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-3 group-hover:scale-125"/>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b group-hover:from-black/70 group-hover:via-black/60 group-hover:to-black/70"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex translate-y-[60%] flex-col items-center justify-center px-9 text-center transition-all duration-500 group-hover:translate-y-0">
          <h1 class="font-dmserif text-3xl font-bold dark:text-[#e4aa0f] text-black group-hover:text-white ">Reservas Confirmadas</h1>
          <p class="mb-3 text-lg italic text-white opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100">Garantizamos la confirmación inmediata de tus reservas, brindándote tranquilidad y certeza desde el momento de la planificación.</p>
          <button class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 py-2 px-3.5 font-com text-sm capitalize text-white shadow shadow-black/60">See More</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative dark:bg-[#7f3812]/30 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center overflow-hidden transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
        <div class="h-96 w-72">
          <Reason3 class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-3 group-hover:scale-125" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b group-hover:from-black/70 group-hover:via-black/60 group-hover:to-black/70"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex translate-y-[60%] flex-col items-center justify-center px-9 text-center transition-all duration-500 group-hover:translate-y-0">
          <h1 class="font-dmserif text-3xl font-bold dark:text-[#e4aa0f] text-black group-hover:text-white ">Viaje Seguro</h1>
          <p class="mb-3 text-lg italic text-white opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100">Priorizamos tu seguridad en cada aspecto del viaje, desde la selección de destinos hasta la implementación de protocolos para asegurar una experiencia sin preocupaciones.</p>
          <button class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 py-2 px-3.5 font-com text-sm capitalize text-white shadow shadow-black/60">See More</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative dark:bg-[#7f3812]/30 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center overflow-hidden transition-shadow hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/30">
        <div class="h-96 w-72">
          <Reason4 class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-3 group-hover:scale-125" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b group-hover:from-black/70 group-hover:via-black/60 group-hover:to-black/70"></div>  
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex translate-y-[60%] flex-col items-center justify-center px-9 text-center transition-all duration-500 group-hover:translate-y-0">
          <h1 class="font-dmserif text-3xl font-bold dark:text-[#e4aa0f] text-black group-hover:text-white ">Atención Personalizada</h1>
          <p class="mb-3 text-lg italic text-white opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100">Nuestro equipo dedicado está siempre a tu disposición, ofreciendo asesoramiento personalizado para crear itinerarios adaptados a tus preferencias y necesidades individuales.</p>
          <button class="rounded-full bg-neutral-900 py-2 px-3.5 font-com text-sm capitalize text-white shadow shadow-black/60">See More</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>
  